properties.areaDesc: Ventura County Mountains; Los Angeles County Mountains excluding the Santa Monica Range
properties.headline: Wind Advisory issued February 3 at 8:52PM PST until February 5 at 9:00AM PST by NWS Los Angeles/Oxnard CA
properties.description:
* WHAT...Northeast winds 25 to 35 mph with gusts 45 to 55 mph
expected, strongest over the Los Angeles County Mountains.

* WHERE...Ventura and Los Angeles County Mountains.

* WHEN...Until 9 AM PST Wednesday.

* IMPACTS...Gusty winds will blow around unsecured objects and
make driving difficult, especially for high profile vehicles.
Tree limbs could be blown down and a few power outages may
result.

* ADDITIONAL DETAILS...The wind, in combination with low
temperatures, will result in wind chill readings between 0 to -5
degrees in many areas.
properties.instruction:
Use extra caution when driving, especially if operating a high
profile vehicle. Secure outdoor objects.

NWSheadline: WIND ADVISORY REMAINS IN EFFECT UNTIL 9 AM PST WEDNESDAY
